 | 2026-04-14 | presentation_surfaces_ui_pipeline_20260405 | Promo capture job loads a pre-rendered image from `source_bundle/promo.png`; actual gameplay capture would require a running game or scene-render replay path that is not yet implemented. | High | Open | The promo workflow is defined but the replay/render capture path is stubbed; real promo derivation needs the candidate-loop scene renderer or a game-runtime capture integration. |
 | 2026-04-16 | review_queue_foundation_20260405 | Review app serves server-rendered HTML but has no image file serving; preview placeholders show "Preview" text instead of actual images. | Medium | Open | Serve static files from REVIEW_APP_ROOT or configure a static file mount in FastAPI; currently templates just show placeholder text. |
 | 2026-04-16 | review_queue_foundation_20260405 | No authentication on review app; any user can approve/reject candidates. | High | Open | Add authentication middleware or IP allowlist for production use. |
 | 2026-04-16 | review_queue_foundation_20260405 | Seed fixtures are not automatically loaded; new deployments start with empty queue. | Low | Open | Add a --seed flag to the startup or an admin endpoint to load fixtures. |
+| 2026-04-17 | prompt_to_asset_program_planner_20260405 | Planner provider interface is defined but no concrete implementation exists yet (OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.). | Medium | Open | Provider abstraction allows swapping implementations; actual API calls need credentials and implementation. |

